 the learning so the lesson is difficult to accept. For this reason, technology greatly affects student learning achievement. Every teacher/lecturer will want all his students/students to be easy to accept learning. Teaching methods and teaching media are important in the learning process so that students can understand the material well. The results of this analysis relate to the ability to understand Arabic language material at the Mahmud Yunus Batusangkar State Islamic University with six questions. The researcher obtained data


