Adam Mudinillah is a lecturer who teaches instructional media courses in the Islamic Religious Education department at the Al-Hikmah ParianganBatusangkar Islamic High School Campus and also as a lecturer at the Islamic State University of Mahmud Yunus Batusangkar with Media and Learning Technology courses at the Tarbiyah Faculty of Teacher Training. He is also often asked as a speaker related to digital-based learning media. He can be contacted at email: adammudinillah@staialhikmahpariangan.ac.id.
Wasehudin Wasehudin is a lecturer in the Islamic Education study program, Faculty of Islamic Studies, Universitas Islam Negeri Sultan Maulana Hasanuddin Banten. Completed his undergraduate education in Islamic Education at Universitas Islam Negeri Sunan GunungDjati, Bandung. Master studies in Islamic Education at Universitas Islam Indonesia, Yogyakarta. Doctoral studies in Islamic Education at Universitas Islam Negeri Sunan GunungDjati, Bandung. In addition to being an Islamic education lecturer, he also serves as Head of study program Islamic Education at Postgraduate Universitas Islam Negeri Sultan Maulana Hasanuddin Banten, is an Islamic education researcher, and actively writes articles about Islamic Education that have been published in several scientific journals. He can be contacted at email: wasehudin@uinbanten.ac.id.
