Amrina Amrina is a senior lecturer who teaches Arabic learning materials at the Islamic State University of Mahmud Yunus Batusangkar, currently not in the stage of submitting to a professor. She was the best graduate while studying for a doctoral program at the State Islamic University of Sjech M. Djamil Djambek Bukittinggi. She also wrote many books about learning Arabic. She can be contacted at email: amrina@uinmybatusangkar.ac.id.
